Package com.hybris.cis.common.ws

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Wss4jUserAndPasswordHandler.Wss4jCredentialsProvider
    Interface for WS credentials.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContextCredentialsProvider
    Adapter Wss4jUserAndPasswordHandler.Wss4jCredentialsProvider reading from the cis context to provide dynamic lookup of the user name and password setting.
    MarshallingWebServiceMessageCallback
    A WebServiceMessageCallback that marshalls an object to the web service messages payload and logs the output to a specific logger.
    SecuredJaxbUnmarshaller
    A Jaxb2Marshaller with XXE prevention.
    StreamingJaxbUnmarshaller
    A JaxbMarshaller for unmarshalling streams.
    UnmarshallingWebServiceMessageExtractor<T>
    A WebServiceMessageExtractor that logs and unmarshalls the web service message's payload.
    URIUtils  
    Wss4jUserAndPasswordHandler
    Implementation of a ClientInterceptor and CallbackHandler to dynamically provide user name and password with the support of a Wss4jUserAndPasswordHandler.Wss4jCredentialsProvider.
